  "description": "<p><strong>近日美国联合航空公司对旗下正在运营的波音737-800飞机进行了改装测试，重新安装的分离式弯刀小机翼已经完成了首轮试飞，在飞行过程中能够减少2% 燃油的消耗，此外还能够改进提高波音737的能源利用率。</strong>美国联合航空公司决定未来将会在包括波音757和767飞机上进行改造，每年单单燃油就能节省2 亿美元的开支。难以置信的是仅仅在在机翼上添加一些金属和小机翼就能大大改善燃油效率节省燃料，当然前期的改进研发投入肯定不止这么点。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ee999b6/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245369.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4%E8%8A%82%E7%9C%812%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%94%E8%88%AA%E4%B8%BA%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3737%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%8F%E6%9C%BA%E7%BF%BC%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245369.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4%E8%8A%82%E7%9C%812%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%94%E8%88%AA%E4%B8%BA%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3737%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%8F%E6%9C%BA%E7%BF%BC%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245369.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4%E8%8A%82%E7%9C%812%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%94%E8%88%AA%E4%B8%BA%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3737%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%8F%E6%9C%BA%E7%BF%BC%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245369.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4%E8%8A%82%E7%9C%812%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%94%E8%88%AA%E4%B8%BA%E6%B3%A2%E9%9F%B3737%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%8F%E6%9C%BA%E7%BF%BC%E